    "title": "京东开放平台宠物健康类目资质标准",
    "followRuleId": "907471693356863488",
    "content": "<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"width: 100.0%; border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 1.0cm;\">\n<td style=\"width: 7.66%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0cm;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"7%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">一级类目</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.64%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0cm;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">二级类目</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.6%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0cm;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"38%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">行业资质</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 41.1%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0cm;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"41%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">特殊资质及要求</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 31.2pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 7.66%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 31.2pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"7%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">宠物健康</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.64%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 31.2pt;\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">宠物营养保健</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 31.2pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"38%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 41.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 31.2pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"41%\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">旗舰店只接受1级以内授权，专卖店、专营店需有3级以内（包括3级）的完整授权链路。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">报关单（经营进口商品）：近四年内的中华人民共和国海关进口货物报关单，报关单上应展现对应品牌名称及商品名称。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.TM</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">标申请时间至入驻审核时间必须大于3个月，TM标有效期请填写申请日期+2年后的日期，R标有效期按商标注册证有效日期填写。</span> </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 31.2pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.64%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 31.2pt;\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">宠物医药器械</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 31.2pt;\" width=\"38%\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">经营国产兽药需提供兽药经营许可证，实际经营商品应在经营许可范围之内。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 31.2pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.64%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 31.2pt;\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">宠物医疗服务</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 31.2pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"38%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">经营动物诊疗服务需要提供动物诊疗许可证。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 31.2pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 100.0%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 31.2pt;\" colspan=\"4\" width=\"100%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.6pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">旗舰店授权书模板：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/926-4279.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; color: blue;\">旗舰店授权书模板</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.6pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">卖场店授权书模板：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/1000-44485.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; color: blue;\">卖场店授权模板</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.6pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东开放平台各类目资费一览表：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; color: blue;\">京东开放平台类目资费规则</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.6pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">店铺命</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">名规则：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; color: blue;\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">附则</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东商家的行为，发生在本管理标准生效之日以前的，适用当时的标准。发生在本管理标准生效之日以后的，适用本标准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东可根据平台运营情况随时调整本管理标准并向商家公示。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本标准已有规定的，适用于本标准。本标准尚无规定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本规则标准于2024年11月19日发布，于2024年11月26日生效。</span></p>",
